Title: Kill Kher Shan
Description:
Kher Shan is one big dooker.

Grooked all my sons! Ick Ick, Nab Nab, Eet Eet, Bitty Bitty, and the others I can't remember.

Wikket wanna help hozen? Go grook Kher Shan!

The dooker's over there.

<Nibi Nibi points to the east.>
ObjectivesText: Kill Kher Shan in Tigers' Wood.
